PLAY INSTRUMENT: Playing a musical instrument

Category: Creative
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Skilled performance on a musical instrument of the character's
choice, chosen when the skill is learned. A second instrument
requires learning the skill again separately.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, singing, art
